v.大声地啜喝 【英】 v. 大声地啜喝(drink with the sound of noisy sucking) 【例】 stop slurping v. 大声地吃喝(吃喝时弄出的很大的吮吸声音) 【记】吃饭slurp是说话就会slur. 【记】音：嗍了盆，吃东西嗍了嗍喽盘子或盆子，嗍(suo)指吮吸 slurp (v.)  1640s, from Dutch slurpen, perhaps of imitative origin (compare German schlürfen). Related: Slurped; slurping. The noun is first recorded 1949, from the verb.
